# Job Tracker Dashboard

A full-stack job tracking dashboard built with **React**, **Next.js**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Prisma**.

## 🔍 Features
- Add, edit, and delete job entries (CRUD)
- Filter jobs by status (applied, interviewing, etc.)
- Sort by date or status
- LocalStorage support for persistence
- Dark mode toggle
- Animated UI with modern design

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Frontend: React, Next.js, Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Prisma, Next.js API routes
- Styling: Tailwind CSS, PostCSS
- State Management: useState, useEffect, localStorage

